Flow of Energy under Echo system
====================================
Every instance(wave/particle/composite of object) of this universe is under streaming, the event of transformation of particles/objects or transmission of waves is due to streaming only.
ie the energy always flow from one form to another form(ie particles/mass) or from one place to another place(ie waves).

The flow of energy can be distinguish in two ways withing life and  beyond the life.
Beyond the life flow of energy may or may not follow the echo system but withing life it follow echo systems.

Beyond the life(ie within nature)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
One can observe the flow of energy every moment every place where ever one observe.Each and every event occur in front of us is due to exchange of energy only and the action behind the hole process of exchange of energy can be observe/feel but unable to explain at extreme level of streaming, but it can be explain in normal form of word.

Flow of energy Follow echo system.
-----------------------------------------------
When the energy flow from one object continuously to its environment the object will be disappear if the energy will not come back to it in any form but the object never disappear, it just change their state(visible/invisible), ie energy must back to it in any other form.
Ex-
-Every moment the sun transmit sunlight(wave form of energy), if one assume sun is complete a object, it must absorb the energy from it environment for continuous transmission.(echo system)

If not then it will become the planet of stone after billion of year(non echo system).

Within the life
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
One can observe in day to day life the request and response activity of lives.
What is this request/response in the form of energy? It is just the flow of energy in echo system.
Request goes with understanding of request only,one may or may not understand the request clearly doesn't matter.

Ex-
Romance between two lives.
Romance with self
Feeling the form of energy  
Feeling some one is mine or i am for them

ie Overall action/reaction of lives flow the echo system of the flow of energy.
.
***Streaming of energy is the center of transformation***
 
 